com.complexible.stardog.api.versioning

Interface VersionFinder


  • public interface VersionFinder
    Utility class for searching the version history. This class lets users define the search criteria and retrieve all the versions matching that criteria.
    Since:
    2.2
    Version:
    4.0
    Author:
    Evren Sirin
